"```sql\nSELECT st.translation\nFROM cards c\nJOIN set_translations st ON c.setCode = st.setCode\nWHERE c.name = 'Ancestor''s Chosen' AND st.language = 'Korean';\n```\n\nThis SQL query selects the translation of the set that contains the card \"Ancestor's Chosen\" in the Korean language. It joins the `cards` table with the `set_translations` table using the `setCode` and filters the results based on the card name and language."